          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "# Multi-Messenger Event Dashboard\n\nThis dashboard displays gravitational wave events and their electromagnetic counterparts.\n\n## Legend:\n\n🔵 **Blue markers** - GW events without EM counterparts\n🔴 **Red markers** - Multi-messenger events (GW + GRB/Optical)\n\n## Data Source:\n\nEvents are fetched in real-time from the REST API at `http://localhost:8080/api/events`\n\nClick on any marker to see event details including:\n- Event ID and SNR\n- False Alarm Rate\n- Associated GRB detections\n- Associated optical transients\n\n## Current Events:\n\nThe database currently contains famous multi-messenger events including **GW170817** - the first detected neutron star merger with EM counterparts!",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
