        "content": "# API Endpoints\n\n## Query Events:\n```bash\ncurl http://localhost:8080/api/events | jq\n```\n\n## Get Specific Event:\n```bash\ncurl http://localhost:8080/api/events/G170817 | jq\n```\n\n## Add New Event:\n```bash\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/events \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{...}'\n```\n\n## Add Detection:\n```bash\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/events/G170817/optical \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{...}'\n```",
